Name: GEOGRAPHICAL ENTITY
Explanation: THE DISTINGUISHING LETTERS INCLUDED IN GEOGRAPHICAL ENTITIES SHALL BE USED WHENEVER IT IS NECESSARY TO USE ABBREVIATIONS IN PUBLICATIONS, DOCUMENTS, ORDERS OR OTHER MEDIA, TO IDENTIFY GEOGRAPHICAL ENTITIES, NATIONS OR ANY PART OF COUNTRIES FORCES (STANAG 1059, PARA 2).

Name: COUNTRY OF BIRTH
Explanation: THE COUNTRY IN WHICH THE PERSON BEING REPORTED WAS BORN.

Name: ALLEGIANCE
Explanation: COUNTRY TO WHICH A PERSON, UNIT, OR PLACE OWES THEIR OR ITS ALLEGIANCE. [REF: STANAG 2438, 2439, 2440, AINTP-3]

Name: PRODUCTION COUNTRY
Explanation: IDENTIFIES THE COUNTRY IN WHICH THE EQUIPMENT WAS MANUFACTURED.

Name: ITEM COUNTRY CODE
Explanation: THIS IS THE COUNTRY THAT THE MATERIAL IS EITHER BEING IMPORTED FROM OR EXPORTED TO.

Name: COUNTRY PROVIDING FOREIGN TECHNOLOGY
Explanation: INDICATES THE COUNTRY THAT PROVIDES FOREIGN TECHNOLOGY TO A PRODUCTION FACILITY.

Name: ALTERNATE ALLEGIANCE
Explanation: THE COUNTRY OR POLITICAL ENTITY TO WHICH THE ENTITY ALSO OWES ALLEGIANCE, POSSIBLY IN CONFLICT WITH OR IN ADDITION TO THE PRIME OR FIRST ALLEGIANCE.

Name: START POINT COUNTRY
Explanation: IDENTIFIES THE COUNTRY WHERE THE ROUTE START POINT IS LOCATED.

Name: RELEASE POINT COUNTRY
Explanation: IDENTIFIES THE COUNTRY WHERE THE ROUTE RELEASE POINT IS LOCATED.

Name: CONTROL CROSSING POINT COUNTRY
Explanation: IDENTIFIES THE COUNTRY WHERE THE ROUTE CONTROL/CROSSING POINT IS LOCATED.

Name: HALT POINT COUNTRY
Explanation: IDENTIFIES THE COUNTRY WHERE THE ROUTE HALT POINT IS LOCATED.

Name: NATIONALITY OF BROADCAST, TWO LETTER CODE
COUNTRY OF EMITTER
Explanation: THE 2-LETTER COUNTRY CODE FOR THE NATION TO WHICH THE DESIGNATED EMITTER BELONGS (STANAG 1059, PARA 2).
